file_content.text: My purpose here is finished. What comes next is pleasure.
I can taste your fear. Soon I will taste your blood!
I have seen beyond death. You think I fear you?
Hah! This is better than I could have imagined!
You are insects to me now! I do not feel your pathetic stings!
I am above pain! I am above fear! I am death given form!
My blood boils! I can feel the power. It wants to be free!
There will be no return for you. Only broken bones and spilled blood!
Are you too stupid to fear me? Is that why you throw yourselves blindly under my heel?
The rest will join you soon!
Masters! I have claimed another for your glory!
Masters! The power wanes! I crave more!
We have no use for a tool that continues to break. Your purpose is fulfilled.
No! You chose me! I'm the one! Don't abandon me... masters!
